Speaker 2: I want to stop it.

Speaker 1: Hello?

Speaker 2: I want to stop the phone.

Speaker 1: Okay.

Speaker 2: Just as long as you understand that if I cancel your account today, sir,

Speaker 1: it's going to cancel that prescription with refills and you won't be able to order again.

Speaker 2: You'll also lose your VIP status, which means when you call back in,

Speaker 1: we won't be able to guarantee the same pricing that you have due to the high demand.

Speaker 2: No problem.

Speaker 1: Cancel it.

Speaker 2: Thank you.

Speaker 1: Okay.

Speaker 2: You're all set.

Speaker 1: Have a great day.

Speaker 2: All right.

Speaker 1: Bye.
